{"word":"μεγαλωστί","slug":"μεγαλωστί","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μεγαλωστί</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>epic and ionic <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> of <a href='S:μέγας'><el>μέγας</el></a>,\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>far and wide, over a vast space</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>= <a href='S:μεγάλως'><el>μεγάλως</el></a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b> 2. also = <el>μεγαλοπρεπῶς</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}